{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": [{"type": "tool_result", "content": "Exit code 1\n---\n---\n# Robust Speech Recognition via Large-Scale Weak Supervision\narXiv: 2212.04356\nAuthors: Alec Radford, Jong Wook Kim, Tao Xu, Greg Brockman, Christine McLeavey, Ilya Sutskever\nYear: 2022 | Venue: \nTopic: asr\nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. Scaling weakly supervised speech recognition to 680,000 hours of multilingual and multitask data enables robust zero-shot transfer without fine-tuning.\n  2. Demonstrating that zero-shot Whisper models approach human-level accuracy and robustness on English speech recognition benchmarks.\n  3. Introducing a single multitask format using special tokens to jointly train a unified model for speech recognition, translation, language identification, and voice activity detection.\n  4. Developing effective decoding heuristics, such as temperature fallback and timestamp constraints, to reliably transcribe long-form audio.\n  5. Releasing the Whisper models and inference code to serve as a foundation for future research on robust speech processing.\n\nTags: ASR, ASR/训练-弱监督\n---\nPaper 2111.09296 not found", "is_error": true, "tool_use_id": "chatcmpl-tool-bc8ca189b9c994d7"}]}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "92502239-0065-4f95-aea8-a07cb5e9037c", "uuid": "65a808d8-dc22-4cb6-9d58-f78e4abc897e", "timestamp": "2026-07-07T13:34:21.949Z", "tool_use_result": "Error: Exit code 1\n---\n---\n# Robust Speech Recognition via Large-Scale Weak Supervision\narXiv: 2212.04356\nAuthors: Alec Radford, Jong Wook Kim, Tao Xu, Greg Brockman, Christine McLeavey, Ilya Sutskever\nYear: 2022 | Venue: \nTopic: asr\nStatus: unread\n\nContributions:\n  1. Scaling weakly supervised speech recognition to 680,000 hours of multilingual and multitask data enables robust zero-shot transfer without fine-tuning.\n  2. Demonstrating that zero-shot Whisper models approach human-level accuracy and robustness on English speech recognition ben